    <item>
      <title>叛军声称夺取刚果城市，卢旺达债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/rwanda-bonds-slip-as-rebel-group-claims-to-seize-congolese-city</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢旺达美元债券周一下跌，此前与卢旺达结盟的叛军组织表示，已占领刚果民主共和国一个重要贸易中心，这加大了这两个中非国家爆发全面战争的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/rwanda-bonds-slip-as-rebel-group-claims-to-seize-congolese-city</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 12:22:26 GMT</pubDate>
